# D{{N}} — Aggregate Conceptual Model

**Audience:** Engineer (uses exact glossary terms).
**When to look at this:** When you need to reason about which entities live together, what's referenced by ID, and where transactional consistency boundaries fall.
**Prose gap closed:** Glossary defines terms one-by-one; canvases describe them per BC; this diagram shows their **relationships and cardinalities** in one frame.

