## Legend

| Notation | Meaning |
|----------|---------|
| `Class { +attr }` | Class with attributes (entity or aggregate root) |
| `*--` | Composition (child cannot exist without parent) |
| `-->` | Association by ID reference |
| `<<value object>>` | Stereotype: no identity, equality by value |
| Note "BC: <name>" | Which bounded context owns this aggregate |

